<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
The code fragment is inside the #else branch of #if MHD_VERSION >= 0x00097701. In the project MHD_VERSION is defined as 0x01000100 which is >= 0x00097701, so the #if branch is always taken and the #else branch (the shown fragment) is never compiled/used. Therefore that code is effectively unreachable in this project configuration.
</scenario>
